 + CTA\n\nCONTENT PREP:\n\u25a1 Write 20 reel scripts using 3 templates\n\u25a1 Film first batch of 10 reels\n\u25a1 Create 5 carousel posts for feed\n\u25a1 Design Story templates in Canva\n\nACCOUNTS:\n\u25a1 Stan Store setup ($29/mo)\n\u25a1 Canva Pro for templates\n\u25a1 CapCut Pro for editing\n\u25a1 Calendly for booking","originalText":"INFRASTRUCTURE:\n\u25a1 ManyChat Pro setup + 3 keyword automations\n\u25a1 Lead magnet creation (P.O.W.E.R. Guide PDF)\n\u25a1 Brand kit design (colors, fonts, logo overlay)\n\u25a1 Filming station setup (ring light, clean BG, mic)\n\u25a1 Bio rewrite with credentials + CTA\n\nCONTENT PREP:\n\u25a1 Write 20 reel scripts using 3 templates\n\u25a1 Film first batch of 10 reels\n\u25a1 Create 5 carousel posts for feed\n\u25a1 Design Story templates in Canva\n\nACCOUNTS:\n\u25a1 Stan Store setup ($29/mo)\n\u25a1 Canva Pro for templates\n\u25a1 CapCut Pro for editing\n\u25a1 Calendly for booking","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","seed":243,"versionNonce":0,"isDeleted":false,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":85,"angle":0,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},{"type":"rectangle","id":"phase1","x":810,"y":4415,"width":740,"height":850,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","backgroundColor":"#dbe4ff","seed":244,"versionNonce":0,"isDeleted":false,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"roundness":{"type":3}},{"type":"text","id":"phaset1","x":825,"y":4425,"width":710,"height":28,"text":"PHASE 2: CONTENT ENGINE","originalText":"PHASE 2: CONTENT ENGINE","fontSize":22,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"autoResize":true,"lineHeig